org.xtext.project.turn.turn

Interface LinearConversion

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, IndicatorConversion, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, URNmodelElement
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    LinearConversionImpl

    public interface LinearConversion
extends URNmodelElement, IndicatorConversion
    A representation of the model object 'Linear Conversion'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Name
    • Long Name
    • Unit
    • Target Value
    • Threshold Value
    • Worst Value
